data.description: Open House December 9th 2pm-4pm. Conveniently Close To Lone Oak  This 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Home Situated On Over An Acre Of Private Land In The County. Enter Through Vaulted Foyer & Into The Oversized & Window-filled Living Room. Enjoy The Formal Dining Room That Leads It To The Eat-in Kitchen That Features Tons Of Natural Light, Double Pantries, & French Doors Leading To Screened Porch, Perfect For Enjoying Views. The 1st Floor Features Large Utility Room, 1/2 Bath, & An Extra Large Bedroom W/ Private Entrance & Outdoor Seating Area. The 2nd Floor Features The Primary Bed & Bath Suite,  W/ Walk-in Closet & Balcony And Bedrooms Three And Four. This Home Presents An Ideal Combination Of Space, Convenience And A Country Side Vibe.
